Geek Feminist Revolution by Kameron Hurley EPUB

As geek culture goes mainstream - from Game of Thrones to the Avengers - it's never been more important to look at the role women play in it and the future they're helping to create. And Kameron is the smart, funny, and profane voice we need to guide readers through the world of fandom and the coming revolution in pop culture.
